      "name": "Fantasy Hub Operators",
      "description": "Operators based in Russia advertise and sell Fantasy Hub via a Malware-as-a-Service model, providing documentation, videos, and subscription management through Telegram bots. They target financial institutions and general Android users.",
      "aliases": [
        "FantasyHub Sellers",
        "Fantasy Hub Threat Actors"
      ],
